articles.description: The Patriots' offensive line is allowing the second-highest pressure rate through four games since 2016. Can they stop the trend against the Dolphins?

images.name: 241006 Bears [1296x729]
images.caption: Bears rookie QB Caleb Williams found DJ Moore (2) on five of eight targets for 105 yards and two TDs vs. the Panthers. "DJ is such a special player," Williams said. "... We were both like, 'Finally, we were able to hit something like that.'"

images.name: Caleb Williams, DJ Moore link up for another TD connection
images.caption: DJ Moore hauls in his second touchdown catch of the game from Caleb Williams to increase the Bears' lead before halftime.

articles.description: Caleb Williams led the Bears' offense past the 400-yard mark for the first time this season, and he established the big-play connection with DJ Moore that he had wanted.
articles.headline: Bears' Caleb Williams finds big-play connection with DJ Moore
